name: Dos Esposas Panda!!!
description: "On his way from China, our Pandaz friend had a layover on the West Coast and was starving! First restaurant he saw was the famous Dos Esposas Restaurante and headed inside. He saw they were preparing to offer two new menu items $CHIPS and $QUESO! He was so excited that he decided to stay and promote them! As an honorary staff member, Pandaz has been given the authorization to help release two new menu items at the restaurant, $CHIPS and $QUESO! This is a fundaraiser auction of a PANDAZ NFT where proceeds will be split between Dos Esposas and Ziggo511. The winner of this auction will become the only owner of (for now!) and be a whale in either $CHIPS or $QUESO!!!!
